snippet.description:
Armaan Music Presenting You The New Odia Romantic Full Music Video song " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " Starring By Rupa & Pintu . This Romantic Hit Track sung By Udit Narayan & Ira Mohanty . This Odia Music Video " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " Is Directed By Somio R , Penned By Panchanan Nayak And Music By Your All Time Favorite Japani Bhai .Please Enjoy And Share Rupa & Pintu New Odia Album Song " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " . We Hope This Romantic Song Must Be a Big Hit .

Audio Credits

Song - Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora
Lyrics - Panchanan Nayak
Music - Japani Bhai
Singer - Udit Narayan & Ira Mohanty
Keyboard Programming - Jaga Jd
Rythm - Anil Das
Recording Studio - RT Studio ( Mumbai ) & Milan Studio
Recordist - Rupak Thakur & Soubhagya Panda
Mixing & Mastering - Milan Das
Special Thanks - Bibek & Ashutosh

Video Credits

Starring - Rupa & Pintu
Direction - Somio R

Travells - Anil
Production Incharge - Debadatta Panda
Special Thanks - Omm

"Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora"
Lyrics:-

Mukhuda:-
**************
M:-
Aji phagunare lagigala ranga
              Sei ranga aji deigala daga

Cross:-
Hrudaya jadi delu tu mate
       De kahile debi mu tate, tope sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(୦)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu 
                 Ajithu mora.....(୦)



Antara:-01
***************
M:-
Piladine gote kahani te sunithili
       Aakasha deshare pari tie thae boli
           Tu sei pari, aji janigali

F:-
Kebe dine gote kabita te padhithili
         Sagara majhire raja tie rahe boli
               Tu sei raja, aji chinhi gali

Cross:-
M:-
Chhatire tate rakhibaa pain
        Sata sagara asichi dein, debi sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(01)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu
                 Ajithu mora.....(01)

Antara:-02
**************
F:-
Dinaku dina mu saja hue beshi kain 
   Aina kahuchi to pari sundari nahi
           Mu bodhe to bata, rahichi chahi

M:-
Aakasha taa aji pruthibi ku chhuindela
      Nijathu nijara kehi jane miligala
            To bata mo bata, gotie hela

Cross:-
F:-
 Manaku gote mana milila
      Aau ja khali baki rahila, tope sindura

Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(02)

snippet.title: Indians And Exercise | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
Find your meaningful connection on happn : http://gethap.pn/aoHj

This Video shows all the crazy fun things that happens while exercising . Indians and Exercise we all have been there in different phases of our fitness journey incidents like  Single people going to gym , parks for workout , jog and suddenly meeting their love . Great for single guys and single girls for becoming fitness couple . Early morning walks with sister . Siblings going to parks like bonta , doing trekking and hiking , playing badminton . Enjoying healthy lifestyle coconut water with malai , vegetable juice , fruit juices , karela juice , chai tapri , tea and bread pakoda ,  eating neem leaves neem datun . Foodie Aunty going on diet to loose weight , controlling the urge to eating oily sugary atta halwa . Skipping sugar , oil , going on morning walks , avoiding cheat meals . Waking up early the 4 AM club to exercise . 2.0 version of friend she is so dedicated to change her body , workout clothes shopping , having every athletic brand nike addidas , puma , gym tights , sports bra , shoes , running , jogging , stretching and then workout motivation goes down in one day . Aunties Uncles laughing in park , joining free yoga classes . Girls and Girl things and their workout fashion . Yoga teacher frustrated with the class , helping the clients to loose weight , treat cervical , back pain , High Blood Pressure , doing pranayam , kapal bhati , yogasanas , aunty sleeping in shav asana and snoring , doing jel neti  , enjoying aerobics with friends , eating out after classes , so much more about the gym freaks , workout freaks , 
Do Share it with everyone, Comment your fav part and like krdena Video guys.. Subscribe the Channel for more amazing videos . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family  .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and  

Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Follow Us On Instagram For more updates about us 

Paayal Jain : https://www.instagram.com/thepaayalja... 
Tena Jaiin : https://www.instagram.com/tenajaiin/?...

Cast : Tena Jaiin , Paayal Jain , Harshita Khinchi , Yash Kaushik 

Script By , Direction By , Screenplay By : Paayal Jain , Tena Jaiin
Dop : Imran Khan

snippet.title: #Video | नागिन | Nagin | #Trending Star Khesari Lal Yadav | Shweta Sharma |  Bhojpuri Gaana
snippet.description:
#khesari भईया #Trending list पे फिर से छाने को है बिलकुल तैयार!.आशीर्वाद दो बेशुमार..अब होगा मज़ा दोगुना और #Nagin की फनकार!

ख़रीदिए कारवाँ मोबाइल- 1500 प्रीलोडिड गानों वाला कीपैड फ़ोन धमाकेदार साउंड के साथ
http://sarega.ma/ycmbuy

Credits: -

🎤Singer - Khesari Lal Yadav & Khushi Kakkar
💃🏻Feat - Shweta Sharma
✍ Lyrics - Arjun Sharma
✂ Edit - Rohan (R Ninja )
🎶Music - Arya Sharma
🎥Video Director - Sooraj Katoch
✂ Editor -  R.Ninja (Rohan Raut) &  Shrikant (ZAV Studio)
🙏EP - Sitosh Yadav
🎥DOP - Yogesh Singh
🎥Art Director - Puneet Kapoor
👗Costumes - ZAI Fashion (Reema)
💃🏻Dancers - Zenith Dance Troupe
💃🏻Choreographer - Geeta Tamta
💄Makeup - Govind (Double G)
🎬Production- Nitesh singh
🌈DI - Rohit Singh

Lyrics:

F तुम Attitude मेरे Mood को समझ ना पा ते हो
F तंग आ चुकी हूँ तुझसे तुम बड़ा सता ते हो
F तेरे चक्कर मे ना आउंगी रह लुंगी तेरे बिन
M मैं प्या र से बो लता हूँ तु बन जा ती ना गिन-2
================Music=============
F Boyfriend मेरे हो तुम नखड़े उठा ना पड़ेगा
F मैं जब बुला ऊंगी तुमको एक का ल पे आना पड़ेगा
M तेरे पा पा का मैं ना Servant हूँ
M मैं पढने ली खने वा ला Student हूँ
F चल हट में सा मने से ना मा र बा तो से पिन-2
M हम प्या र से बो लिला त तू बन जा लू ना गिन-2
================Music=============
F मेरी जैसी लड़की अर्जुन ईस जनम में ना मिलेगी
F फूल बन कर तेरे बा हो में को ई और ना खिलेगी
M तेरे का रन रहता हूँ मैं Dipration में
M तू डा ल देती है खेसा री को Tension में

F छो डूंगी पच्छा तो गे मैं हूँ छो री नमकी न
M मैं प्या र से बो लता हूँ तु बन जा ती ना गिन-2

snippet.title: Chengiz Official Hindi Teaser | Jeet | Susmita | Rohit Roy | Shataf | Neeraj Pandey | Rajesh Ganguly
snippet.description:
‘Chengiz’ has officially set foot.
Get ready for an action-packed experience as we unveil the Hindi Teaser of #Chengiz. The story of an underworld don whose grip on the city is unbreakable. Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

INGREDIENTS-------
Onion- 2
Carrot- 1/4 Cup
Capsicum- 1/2 Cup
Boiled Egg
Chicken - 300 gm
Ginger- 3/4 Tbsp

Green Chilli- 4
Curry Leaves 
Coriander Leaves-3 Tbsp
Kashmiri Red chili powder- 2 Tsp
Pepper Powder- 3/4 Tsp
Chicken Masala-1 Tsp
Turmeric Powder- 1/4 Tsp
Salt
Lemon Juice- 1/2 Tsp
Water- 1 Tbsp

Samosa sheet 

Maida-1/2 cup
Salt
Water
Pepper powder- 1/4 Tsp
Cornflakes OR Bread Crumbs

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 27 Teaser - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 27 Teaser - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

Aaj Phir Jeene ki tamanna hai

Sar se paaon talak dil hai bhola

Saans seene mein hai par thami si lage

Jo bujhe na kabhi ye vo shola

Raaste mein hai magar mushkilein hain badi

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 25 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 25 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 22nd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: BIG ICE CREAM | Biggest Stick ice making | Watermelon ice | Kiwi ice | Milk ice | Fruit ice Making
snippet.description:
In our childhood, we enjoy those moments with tasting stick ice. We call this ice "Kuchi ice". Today in our village, we made the three most giant colorful stick ice with fruits and milk. We made three types of ice cream. The first one is milk. The second is watermelon. The third one is Kiwi.

Childhood memory comes again! Tasty!

snippet.description:
Soft சப்பாத்தி செய்ய 4 முக்கியமான டிப்ஸ் | how to make soft chapati | soft chapati recipe in tamil | gomathi kitchen | சப்பாத்தி செய்வது எப்படி|   மிருதுவான சப்பாத்தி செய்வது எப்படி? | soft chapati |  how to make soft chapati | soft chapati recipe | Soft Chapati | Chapati | சப்பாத்தி | soft chapati recipe in tamil | சப்பாத்தி செய்வது எப்படி | how to make soft chapati | chapati recipe in tamil | chapati | soft chapati | how to make soft chapathi | chapati in tamil | chapati recipe | how to make soft chapati in tamil | soft chapati recipe | how to make chapati in tamil | how to make chapati | chapathi | how to make chapathi | soft chapathi | roti recipe | soft chapati preparation | chapathi recipe in tamil | roti | Chapati Recipe in Tamil | Soft Chapati Recipe in Tamil | How to make soft Chapati in Tamil | சப்பாத்தி சூப்பரா வர இத மட்டும் செய்ங்க | Soft Chapati in Tamil | How to make Soft Chapathi in tamil

I'll walk you through the ingredients you'll need and the step-by-step process to make these delicious chapatis. Whether you're a seasoned cook or just starting out in the kitchen, this recipe is easy to follow and yields great results every time. So grab your apron and let's get started! snippet.title: SITTA SITTENDA KOTTE PART 4 FULL SONG | PARSHURAM NAGAM | SINGER LAVANYA | BODDU DILIP
snippet.description:
SITTA SITTENDA KOTTE PART 4 FULL SONG | PARSHURAM NAGAM | SINGER LAVANYA | BODDU DILIP


రచన&దర్శకత్వం: పరశురాం నాగం
సంగీతం: కాయితోజు ప్రవీణ్ కుమార్
గానం: లావణ్య & బొడ్డు దిలీప్ కుమార్
ట్యూన్ సోర్స్: నరావుల మల్లవ్వ
DOP: హరీష్ పటేల్
ఎడిటింగ్: ఆదర్శ్ పటేల్
నటీనటులు: కార్తిక్ రెడ్డి, మానస,
బిట్టు , హనీ, 
సహనటులు:
పల్లవి, పరశురాం నాగం, 
గంగ శ్రీకాంత్ మాస్టర్
టెక్నికల్ సపోర్ట్: వంశీ S

PRODUCTION: 
MANAIR MUSIC AND MOVIES

ప్రత్యేక ధన్యవాదాలు:
LADDU MUSIC, VIVAAN
ONE TECHNOLOGIES,
వాగ్దేవీ కళాశాల, వేములవాడ
విజేత ఆర్థ్రో హాస్పిటల్, వేములవాడ
RB శరత్ రాజా , వేములవాడ


ప్రత్యేక ధన్యవాదాలు:
నాగం కొమురయ్య మల్లవ్వ
నాగం మౌనిక బాలశేఖర్
గుంటి నరేష్,
అభి, జగిత్యాల
తొంటి లస్మయ్య & ఫ్యామిలీ
పెంటల మహాంకాళి & ఫ్యామిలీ
కోరే దేవయ్య & ఫ్యామిలీ
జమున -తిరుపతి & ఫ్యామిలీ
జోగాపూర్ గ్రామస్తులు & వేములవాడ పురప్రముఖులు


పాట నేపథ్యం:
తలిదండ్రులు తమ పిల్లల్ని  ఎంతో అల్లారు ముద్దుగా... స్కూల్ బస్ లో.. బడికి పంపిస్తారు. 
కానీ.. బస్ డ్రైవర్ ఫోన్ మాట్లాడుతూ ఉంటాడు. ఆ పక్కనే ఐస్ క్రీం ఉంటుంది. దాన్నీ చూసి.. పిల్లాడు ఉరికి వస్తాడు. బస్ వెనక్కి వస్తూండడంతో.. బస్ కింద పడి.. కాలు విరుగుతుంది. అది చూసి అక్క వెనక్కి పరిగెత్తుకుంటు రావడంతో.. తొక్కుడు బండ మీద జారి తల పగులుతుంది. జీవచ్చవాళ్ల ఉన్న పిల్లల్ని చూసి అమ్మానాన్నలు గుండె పగులుతుంది. వెంటనే హాస్పిటల్ కి ఎత్తుకుపోతారు. 
అక్కడ డాక్టర్ గారు చెకప్ చేసి... ఆపరేషన్ చేసి.. బతికిస్తారు. దాంతో.. ఆందరి మొఖాలు ఆనందతాండవం చేస్తాయి.
కథ సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది అనే లోపే... కాలు విరిగి కట్టుతో ఉన్న... పిలవాన్ని తోటి పిల్లలు.. ఆడుకోవడానికి రానివ్వరు. దాంతో పిల్లవాడు బాగా బాధపడతాడు. 
అది గమనించి.. తలిదండ్రులు.. అక్కున చేర్చుకోని ఓదార్చుతారు. మెల్లగా నడకలు నేర్పిస్తారు. అలా అలా కొద్దిరోజుల్లో పిల్లలిద్దరూ సాధారణ స్థితికి వస్తారు. 
మెల్లగా.. జాగ్రత్తగా బడికి వెళ్లడం ప్రారంభిస్తారు. 

దాంతో కథ పరిపూర్ణంగా సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది. మా ఈ ప్రయత్నం మీకు నచ్చితే.. plz Support చేయండి.. షేర్ చేయండి. ధన్యవాదాలు..
మీ పరశురాం నాగం.✍️
రచయిత & దర్శకులు.
MANAIR MUSIC & MOVIES

తొంటి లస్మయ్య & ఫ్యామిలీ
పెంటల మహాంకాళి & ఫ్యామిలీ
కోరే దేవయ్య & ఫ్యామిలీ
జమున -తిరుపతి & ఫ్యామిలీ
జోగాపూర్ గ్రామస్తులు & వేములవాడ పురప్రముఖులు


పాట నేపథ్యం:
తలిదండ్రులు తమ పిల్లల్ని  ఎంతో అల్లారు ముద్దుగా... స్కూల్ బస్ లో.. బడికి పంపిస్తారు. 
కానీ.. బస్ డ్రైవర్ ఫోన్ మాట్లాడుతూ ఉంటాడు. ఆ పక్కనే ఐస్ క్రీం ఉంటుంది. దాన్నీ చూసి.. పిల్లాడు ఉరికి వస్తాడు. బస్ వెనక్కి వస్తూండడంతో.. బస్ కింద పడి.. కాలు విరుగుతుంది. అది చూసి అక్క వెనక్కి పరిగెత్తుకుంటు రావడంతో.. తొక్కుడు బండ మీద జారి తల పగులుతుంది. జీవచ్చవాళ్ల ఉన్న పిల్లల్ని చూసి అమ్మానాన్నలు గుండె పగులుతుంది. వెంటనే హాస్పిటల్ కి ఎత్తుకుపోతారు. 
అక్కడ డాక్టర్ గారు చెకప్ చేసి... ఆపరేషన్ చేసి.. బతికిస్తారు. దాంతో.. ఆందరి మొఖాలు ఆనందతాండవం చేస్తాయి.
కథ సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది అనే లోపే... కాలు విరిగి కట్టుతో ఉన్న... పిలవాన్ని తోటి పిల్లలు.. ఆడుకోవడానికి రానివ్వరు. దాంతో పిల్లవాడు బాగా బాధపడతాడు. 
అది గమనించి.. తలిదండ్రులు.. అక్కున చేర్చుకోని ఓదార్చుతారు. మెల్లగా నడకలు నేర్పిస్తారు. అలా అలా కొద్దిరోజుల్లో పిల్లలిద్దరూ సాధారణ స్థితికి వస్తారు. 
మెల్లగా.. జాగ్రత్తగా బడికి వెళ్లడం ప్రారంభిస్తారు. 

దాంతో కథ పరిపూర్ణంగా సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది. మా ఈ ప్రయత్నం మీకు నచ్చితే.. plz Support చేయండి.. షేర్ చేయండి. ధన్యవాదాలు..
మీ పరశురాం నాగం.✍️
రచయిత & దర్శకులు.

snippet.title: Hyundai Verna SX(O) Turbo 2023- ₹17 lakh | Real-life review
snippet.description:
Namaste friends, please LIKE & SUBSCRIBE :)

The Hyundai Verna, or Hyundai Accent is a subcompact car produced by Hyundai. In Australia, the first generation models carried over the Hyundai Excel name used by the Accent's predecessor. On 13 February 2023, Hyundai released the sixth-generation model as the Verna (BN7) in India on 21 March 2023, featuring Hyundai's 'Sensuous Sportiness' design identity. Its design is inspired by the Elantra. With a total of 17 Level 2 - ADAS features, the all-new Hyundai VERNA creates a new precedent for this segment with Hyundai SmartSense. Further, with this segment’s best in class acoustic experience - Bose Premium Sound 8 Speaker system. #HyundaiVerna #Verna #Hyundai

Petrol: 1497 cc, Inline-4 cylinder, Hyundai Smartstream G1.5 MPi engine, 113 HP Power, 143 Nm Torque, 18 kmpl (Manual), 19 kmpl (Automatic) Average, 45 litre Fuel Tank, 6-speed Manual or IVT Automatic Transmission

Petrol: 1482 cc, Inline-4 cylinder, Hyundai Smartstream G1.5T Turbo GDi engine, 157 HP Power, 253 Nm Torque, 20 kmpl Average, 45 litre Fuel Tank, 6-speed Manual or 7-speed DCT Automatic Transmission

7 Colours: Grey, Tellurian Brown, Silver, Red, White, Black, Starry Night (Roof colour- Black)

7 Variants: EX, S, SX, SX(O), SX Turbo, SX(O) Turbo, SX(O) Turbo DCT

3 Upholsteries: Fabric, Beige Leatherette, Black Leatherette

4 Wheels: 15 inch Steel, 15 inch Alloy, 16 inch Diamond Cut Alloy, 16 inch Black Alloy

Price range: Rs. 10.89 lakh - Rs. 17.37 lakh (Ex-showroom, Delhi)

Lyrics 

Subah subah bana ke chai
Saiyan ji tere le kar aaye
Dekh Neend bhari aankhen teri
Lagta sab kuch wahi tham jaye

Subah subah bana ke chai
Saiyan ji tere le kar aaye
Dekh Neend bhari aankhen teri
Lagta sab kuch wahi tham jaye

Jaise mai deewana tera
Tu meri deewani hogi
Gale mein tere jaan mere
Naam ki nishani hogi

#premkahani #rahulvaidya #dishaparmar 


Kitni khoobsoorat hogi
Teri meri prem kahani ,
Sang mein budhe honge hum
Sang mein beetegi jawaani

Kitni khoobsoorat hogi
Teri meri prem kahani ,
Sang mein budhe honge hum
Sang mein beetegi jawaani

Mujhko lagta hai
Teri bahon me kuch jadu tona hai ,
Main toh tha mitti
mujhko tune chuu ke kar dia Sona hai !

Tum zarori hurdam ho
Hume har pal sath me rehna hai ,
Hasna hai Hume tere sath me
Tere sath me rona hai !

Aur baaki saari baatein tumko hi seekhani hogi
Roti main paka dunga par tumhe
Hath se khilani hogi !

Kitni khoobsoorat hogi
Teri meri prem kahani ,
Sang mein bhudhe honge hum
Sang mein beetegi jawani !


Pyar pyar tujhe pyar pyar
Haa bachchon ke jaise karunga mai ,
Jaan jaan meri jaan jaan tere liye
Kuch bhi karunga mai !

aansu na mai aane dunga
Aankho me tere ,
Roz tujhko sulaunga
Mere gaane ga ke re !

Mehndi mere naam ki tujhko
Hathon me lagani hogi ,
Subah shaam aur raatein
Tere sath hi suhani hongi !


Kitni khoobsoorat hogi
Teri meri prem kahani ,
Sang mein bhudhe honge hum
Sang mein beetegi jawaani

Credits:

Lyrics: Traditional

जय अम्बे गौरी आरती Lyrics :
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी, मैया जय श्यामा गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri Maiy Jay Ambe Gauri
तुमको निशिदिन ध्यावत, तुमको निशिदिन ध्यावत
Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat
हरि ब्रह्मा शिवरी
Hari Brahma Shivri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

मांग सिंदूर विराजित टीको मृगमद को
Mang Sindoor Virajat Teeko Mrugmad Ko
मैया टीको मृगमद को
Maiya Teeko Mrugmad Ko
उज्ज्वल से दोउ नैना उज्ज्वल से दोउ नैना
Ujjwal Se Dou Naina Ujjwal Se Dou Naina
चंद्रवदन नीको
Chandravadan Neeko
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

कनक समान कलेवर, रक्ताम्बर राजै
Kanak Samaan Kalevar Raktabar Raaje
मैया रक्ताम्बर राजै
Maiya Raktabar Raje
रक्तपुष्प गल माला, रक्तपुष्प गल माला
Raktpushp Gal  Mala Raktpushp Gal Mala
कंठन पर साजै
Kanthan Par Saaje
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

केहरि वाहन राजत, खड्ग खप्पर धारी
Kehari Vahan Rajat Khadag Khappar Dhari
मैया खड्ग खप्पर धारी
Maiya Khadag Khappar Dhari
सुर नर मुनिजन सेवत, सुर नर मुनिजन सेवत
Sur Nar Munijan Sevit Sur Nar Munijan Sevit
तिनके दुखहारी
Tinke Ddukhhaari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

कानन कुण्डल शोभित नासाग्रे मोती
Kanan Kundal Shobhit Nasagre Moti
मैया नासाग्रे मोती 
Maiya Nasagre Moti
कोटिक चंद्र दिवाकर कोटिक चंद्र दिवाकर
Kotik Chandra Divakar Kotik Chandra Divakar
राजत सम ज्योती
Rajat Ssam Jyoti
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

शुंभ निशुंभ बिदारे महिषासुर घाती
Shumbh Nishumbh Bidare Mahishasur Ghaati
मैया महिषासुर घाती
Maiya Mahishasur Ghaati
धूम्र विलोचन नैना, धूम्र विलोचन नैना
Dhoomra Vilochan Naina Dhoomra Vilochan Naina
निशदिन मदमाती
Nishdin Madmati
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

चण्ड-मुण्ड संहारे शोणित बीज हरे
Chand Mund Sanhaare Shonit Beej Hare
मैया शोणित बीज हरे
Maiya Shonit Beej Hare
मधु कैटभ दोउ मारे, मधु कैटभ दोउ मारे
Madhu Kaitabh Dou Maare Madhu Kaitabh Dou Mare
सुर भयहीन करे
Sur Bhyaheen Kare
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

ब्रहमाणी रुद्राणी तुम कमला रानी
Brahmani Roodrani Tum Kamla Rani
मैया तुम कमला रानी
Maiya Tum Kamla Rani
आगम निगम बखानी, आगम निगम बखानी
Aagam Nigham Bakhani Aagam Nigam Bakhani
तुम शिव पटरानी
Tum Shiv Patraani
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

चौंसठ योगिनी गावत नृत्य करत भैरों
Chaunsath Yogini Gaawat Nritya Kare Bbhairo
मैया नृत्य करत भैरों
Maiya Nritya Kare Bhairo
बाजत ताल मृदंगा, बाजत ताल मृदंगा
Baajat Taal Mrudanga Baajat Taal Mrudanga
अरू बाजत डमरू
Aru Baajat Dsamroo
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

तुम ही जग की माता तुम ही हो भरता
Tum Hi Jag Ki Mata Tum Hi Ho Bharta
मैया तुम ही हो भरता
Maiya Tum Hi Ho Bharta
भक्तन की दुख हरता, भक्तन की दुख हरता
Bhaktan Ki Dukh Harta Bhatan Ki Dukh Harta
सुख संपति करता
Sukh Sampati Kartaa
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

भुजा अष्ट अति शोभित वर-मुद्रा धारी
Bhuja Asht Ati Shobhit Var Mudra Dhari
मैया वर मुद्रा धारी
Maiya Var Mudra Dhari
मनवांछित फल पावत, मनवांछित फल पावत
Manvanchhit Phal Paavat Manvanchhit Phal Paavat
सेवत नर नारी
Sevit Nar Naari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

कंचन थाल विराजत अगर कपूर बाती
Kanchan Thal Virajat Agar Kapoor Baati
मैया अगर कपूर बाती
Maiya Agar Kapoor Baati
श्रीमालकेतु में राजत, श्रीमालकेतु में राजत
Shri Malketu Men Rajat Shri Malketu Men Rajat
कोटि रतन ज्योती
Koti Ratan Jjyoti
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

श्री अम्बे जी की आरती जो कोई नर गावे
Shri Ambe Ji Ki Aarti Jo Koyi Nar Gave
मैया जो कोई नर गावे
Maiya Jo Koyi Nar Gave
कहत शिवानंद स्वामी कहत शिवानंद स्वामी
Kahat Shivanand Swami Kahat Shivanand Swami
सुख सम्पति पावे
Sukh Sampti Paave
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri
 
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी, मैया जय श्यामा गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri Maiy Jay Ambe Gauri
तुमको निशिदिन ध्यावत, तुमको निशिदिन ध्यावत
Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat
हरि ब्रह्मा शिवरी
Hari Brahma Shivri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jay Ambe Gauri

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3726 - 23 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3726: Tapu Sena Ki Safalta
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena's creative contribution is mentioned by Asit Kumarr Modi, who announces a foreign trip for them. In the midst of this, Popatlal raises his voice and protests. He expresses his dissatisfaction with Asit Kumarr Modi's failure to take his wedding seriously. Asit Ji promises Popatlal that he will find him a suitable bride soon. Later, the residents of Gokuldham celebrate the occasion with dancing and good food. The following morning, Bapuji seeks help from the Tapu Sena to install the game on his phone. Bhide also expresses gratitude to Tapu Sena. Bhide and Madhavi present Tapu Sena with a box of ladoo to express their compliments. Meanwhile. Jetha worries about his meeting with Ramsong dealers. Stay tuned for more details!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3726, 23 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000214537

http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

Today we are going to see how to make less oily and perfect puri. Puri is generally made on festive days like Gudhi padwa, dasara etc. Today we will make such that will absorb less oil. Yes, here are a few tips to make crispy and fluffy puri that absorbs minimum oil. I will give you few tips and tricks during the video. Puri is a popular puffed Indian bread. It is prepared form wheat flour and deep fried. It is mostly enjoyed on festival days with different Indian desserts. The puries should be fluffy and soft. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
• 2 cups Wheat flour
• Salt to taste
• Water 
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Mix wheat flour and salt well and add a little water at a time to knead stiff dough. 
• Cover and rest the dough for at least 15-20 minutes. 
• Knead the dough well once more until it becomes smooth and even. 
• You can make small dough balls and roll puris from it. 
• Or divide the dough into 2 parts and make one of them smooth and even. It has to be 
  smooth. 
• Keep the left over dough always covered. 
• Roll out a big chapatti from the dough. The chapatti should be even.  
• Avoid use of oil or dry flour while rolling the puri. 
• Make puris with the help of a katori or a lid. 
• Heat up oil on medium heat. 
• While dropping puri in hot oil make sure the smooth side should face downwards and the 
  rolled side should be upper side.
• Drop puri in hot oil and fry well on medium to high heat. 
• Press a little and when lower side is fried well flip the puri over and fry well from other side 
  too. 
• When puri is fried well from other side too, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it into 
  dish. Puri is all ready.
Tips:
• Avoid use of water while kneading the dough. Do not use hot or cold water when you knead 
  dough. 
• Always knead stiff dough. 
• Never make puris immediately after kneading dough. Rest the dough for at least 15-20 
  minutes. 
• Avoid use of oil or dry flour while rolling the puri. 
• Make sure you fry each side of puri once. Avoid flipping puri many times.

Today we are going to see how to make less oily and perfect puri. Puri is generally made on festive days like Gudhi padwa, dasara etc. Today we will make such that will absorb less oil. Yes, here are a few tips to make crispy and fluffy puri that absorbs minimum oil. I will give you few tips and tricks during the video. Puri is a popular puffed Indian bread. It is prepared form wheat flour and deep fried. It is mostly enjoyed on festival days with different Indian desserts. The puries should be fluffy and soft. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
• 2 cups Wheat flour
• Salt to taste
• Water 
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Mix wheat flour and salt well and add a little water at a time to knead stiff dough. 
• Cover and rest the dough for at least 15-20 minutes. 
• Knead the dough well once more until it becomes smooth and even. 
• You can make small dough balls and roll puris from it. 
• Or divide the dough into 2 parts and make one of them smooth and even. It has to be 
  smooth. 
• Keep the left over dough always covered. 
• Roll out a big chapatti from the dough. The chapatti should be even.  
• Avoid use of oil or dry flour while rolling the puri. 
• Make puris with the help of a katori or a lid. 
• Heat up oil on medium heat. 
• While dropping puri in hot oil make sure the smooth side should face downwards and the 
  rolled side should be upper side.
• Drop puri in hot oil and fry well on medium to high heat. 
• Press a little and when lower side is fried well flip the puri over and fry well from other side 
  too. 
• When puri is fried well from other side too, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it into 
  dish. Puri is all ready.
Tips:
• Avoid use of water while kneading the dough. Do not use hot or cold water when you knead 
  dough. 
• Always knead stiff dough. 
• Never make puris immediately after kneading dough. Rest the dough for at least 15-20 
  minutes. 
• Avoid use of oil or dry flour while rolling the puri. 
• Make sure you fry each side of puri once. Avoid flipping puri many times.

snippet.title: Meet Amogh Lila Prabhu | Episode 91
snippet.description:
YouTube Channel: https://youtube.com/@RevivingValues 

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

snippet.title: पर्चे बांटने वाला सरकारी अफ़सर बना, लेकिन... ☝🔥  | @RankersGurukul | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Aditya जी की तरह सच्ची मेहनत से आप भी अपने हर सपने को सच कर सकते हैं: https://joshskills.app.link/4OoZkXe1jyb

Aditya Ranjan is an Excise inspector and also teaches Maths to aspirants preparing for SSC and other Government Exams. He was born in Bihar. His father is a farmer and he was from a poor family. A time also came when he learned to distribute posters on the streets, learn to drive rickshaws,s and even sleep hungry for many nights. Then he started preparing for Government Exams and cracked 5 Government Jobs. He was also very fond of teaching and he also taught home tuition in difficult times, so he chose to teach as a career. Today he gives a lot of knowledge to SSC Aspirants from his classes like SSC CGL strategy, Tips, etc.

Today, through Josh Talks, Aditya Ranjan ji will tell how he achieved success by facing difficulties and will also tell his success story or life story. So do watch this SSC Motivational video by Josh Talks entirely.

Aditya Ranjan जी Excise inspector हैं और साथ में SSC और बाकी Government Exams की preparation कर रहे aspirants को Maths पढ़ाते हैं. इनका जन्म Bihar में हुआ. इनके पिता किसान हैं और ये एक गरीब परिवार से थे. एक समय ऐसा भी आया जब इन्हें सड़कों पर Poster बाटने पढ़े, Rikshaw चलाना पढ़ा और कईं रात भूखा भी सोना पढ़ा. फिर इन्होंने Government Exam की preparation चालू की और 5 Government Job crack की. Teaching का भी इन्हें काफ़ी शौक था और इन्होंने मुश्किल दौर में Home tution भी पढ़ाया तो इन्होंने teaching को as a career चुना. आज ये SSC Aspirants को अपनी classes से काफ़ी knowledge देते हैं जैसे कि SSC CGL strategy, Tips etc. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Aditya Ranjan जी बताएंगे कि कैसे इन्होंने मुश्किलों का सामना करके success को हासिल करा और साथ ही सुनाएंगे अपनी success story. तो जोश Talks की इस SSC Motivational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #AdityaRanjanJoshTalks #Motivation

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi... 

-----**DISCLAIMER**----- 
All of the views and work outside the pretext of the video of the speaker, are his/ her own, and Josh Talks, by any means, does not support them directly or indirectly and neither is it liable for it. Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts. Josh Talks by any means, does not further or amplify any specific ideology or propaganda.

snippet.title: नवरात्रि के तीसरे दिन की माँ चंद्रघंटा की कथा | Navratri Day 3 - Maa chandraghanta ki katha
snippet.description:
नवरात्रि के तीसरे दिन की माँ चंद्रघंटा की कथा | Navratri Day 3 - Maa chandraghanta ki katha

नवरात्रि  के 9 दिन के पावन त्यौहार में  देवी भगवती के नो रूपों की पूजा की जाती है। नवरात्रि के तीसरे दिन मां दुर्गा के चंद्रघंटा स्वरूप की  पूजा की जाती है। दुर्गा मां का यह स्वरूप परम शांतिदायक और कल्याणकारी है। इनके मस्तक में घंटे का आकार का अर्धचंद्र मौजूद है। यही कारण है कि मां के इस स्वरूप को चंद्रघंटा कहा जात है।इस रूप में, उसका रंग सुनहरा है और उनकी दस भुजाएँ  हैं। देवी चंद्रघंटा  ने 9 भुजाओं में एक त्रिशूल, गदा, बाण, धनुष, तलवार, कमल, बकरी, बेल और एक कमंडलु (जल का पात्र)  धारण किए हुए हैं,  और दसवें हाथ से  वह अपने भक्तों को आशीर्वाद  देती हैं।  मां चंद्रघंटा का वाहन सिंह है। इससे पता चलता है कि आदि शक्ति अपने भक्तों के प्रति दया और ममता रखते हुए अपने दुश्मनों के प्रति भयानक हो सकती है। माता चंद्रघंटा के पूजन से भक्तोंको मणिपुर चक्र से जाग्रत होने वाली सिद्धियां स्वत:  ही प्राप्त हो जाती हैं तथा सांसारिक कष्टों से मुक्ति मिलती है।  हमारे शरीर के सात चक्रों में  तीसरे चक्र को नाभि चक्र अथवा मणिपुर चक्र कहा जाता है। यह चक्र पाचन तंत्र को ठीक रखने के साथ  7 मानसिक और आध्यात्मिक भावनाओं को भी शांत रखता है। आइए अब सुनते हैं मां चंद्रघंटा देवी की कथा
और जानते हैं की मां  चंद्रघंटा की पूजा विधि
चंद्रघंटा माता  की कथा से पता चलता है कि देवी चंद्रघंटा कौन है। देवी को चंद्रघंटा का यह नाम कैसे मिला? इस वीडियो में चंद्रघंटा आरती, चंद्रघंटा मंत्र, चंद्रघंटा कवच ​​और चंद्रघंटा स्तोत्रम भी दिखाया गया है।

Nine forms of Goddess Durga are worshiped in the 9 day holy festival of Navratri. Chandraghanta form of Maa Durga is worshiped on the third day of Navratri. This form of Durga Maa is the ultimate peace and welfare. She has a crescent shape on her forehead. That is why this form of mother bhagwati is called Chandraghanta. In this form, her color is golden and she has ten arms. Goddess Chandraghanta holds a trident, mace, arrow, bow,  sword, lotus, goat, bell and a kamandalu (vessel of water) in nine arms, and with the tenth hand she blesses her devotees. The vehicle of mother Chandraghanta is Lion. This shows that Adi Shakti can be terrible towards her enemies but at the same time having compassion and affection for her devotees. With the worship of Mata Chandraghanta, the devotees get awakened their  Manipur Chakra  and automatically get liberated from worldly sufferings. The third chakra in the seven chakras of our body is called Navel Chakra or Manipur Chakra. This chakra keeps the digestive system fine and also keeps the 7 mental and spiritual feelings calm. Now let's hear the story of Mother Chandraghanta Devi And know that the method of worship of mother Chandraghanta 
 Maa Chandraghanta ki katha shows who is chandraghanta mata. How devi got this name of Chandraghanta ? This video also shows Chandraghanta Aarti, Chandraghanta mantra , Chandraghanta kavach, and Chandraghanta stotram.
#चंद्रघंटा #navratri  #chandraghanta

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3725 - 22 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3725: Manoranjan Ka Khazana
--------------------------------------------------------
Asit Kumarr Modi Ji talks about Gokuldham and how it has inspired him to make this creative project, which includes nursery rhymes and digital games. He introduces the games, which are inspired by Gokuldham people like Jethalal and Bhide and his scooter "Sakharam". He promises huge fun and entertainment from these digital projects. Tapu Sena talks about everyone's involvement in developing the apps, like Goli's music, Gogi's graphics, and Pinku's coding. Tapu also gets praised for his leadership skills. Asit Kumarr Modi Ji also talks about launching this project in all regional languages soon because Gokuldham is a melting pot of cultures.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3725, 22 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000214412

snippet.title: चैत्र अमावस्या मंगलवार : पंचमुखी हनुमान की इस चमत्कारी कथा को सुनने से सभी कष्ट, संकट दूर होते है
snippet.description:
#HanumanKatha 
#PanchmukhiHanumanKatha 
#ChaitraAmavasya 
#Amavasya

#bhaktidarshan

#hanumanmantra
#2023HanumanKatha
#bhaktidarshan
#HanumanKatha

 पंचमुखी हनुमान :
धार्मिक मान्यता है कि मंगलवार के दिन जो व्यक्ति हनुमान जी के पंचमुखी रूप की पूजा करते है उनकी समस्त प्रकार की बाधाएं दूर हो जाती हैं। हनुमान जी कलयुग के देवता हैं हनुमान जी भक्त शिरोमणि है हनुमान जी अपने भक्तों से बहुत जल्दी प्रसन्न हो जाते हैं और अपना आशीर्वाद देते हैं। हनुमान जी की पंचमुखी अवतार वाली तस्वीर घर के मुख्य द्वार में लगाने से सभी तरह के सुख और आनंद की प्राप्ति होती है।

हनुमान जी का पंचमुखी अवतार :-
: पहले वानर मुख से सारे दुश्मनों पर विजय मिलती है।
: दूसरे गरुड़ मुख से सारी परेशानियां दूर होती हैं।
: तीसरे उत्तर दिशा के वराह मुख से प्रसिद्धि, शक्ति और लंबी आयु मिलती है।
: चौथे नृसिंह मुख से मुश्किलें, तनाव और डर दूर होते हैं।
: पांचवें अश्व मुख से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं।

भक्ति दर्शन के सुपरहिट भजन/आरतियाँ सुनने के लिए @Bhakti_Darshan को SUBSCRIBE करे व अन्य भक्तों के साथ Share करे व वीडियो को Like करना न भूलें.

snippet.description:
"Iddat" is a movie about a girl who elopes and marries a boy from a different caste. Her husband's actions lead to her life being shattered. Will her family forgive her and accept her back into their lives? The movie explores themes of love, forgiveness, and acceptance in the face of difficult circumstances.

In association with Meena Enterprises

रसिकहो,
मराठीचा स्वाभिमान आयुष्यभर ज्यांनी जपला.. मराठी लोकसंगीत लोककला आंतरराष्ट्रीय पातळीवर ज्यांच्यामुळे पोहोचली..
